stimulus:
Task rules

The experiment is divided into 40 games. Each game consists of 20 days. On each day you can choose to work on 1 project.
  • If you choose Project Cyan , you will end the game and earn the equivalent of safe projects payouts for the remaining days. Daily payout for the safe option is either 0.1 or 0.2 of a penny (¢).
  • If you choose Project Cobalt , you will get a variable amount of Goal Points (GP). If you manage to reach the required amount of points before the deadline, you will be awarded a bonus of 10 pennies (¢) , in addition to the remaining safe payouts from the safe option .
IMPORTANT: choosing the safe project ends the current game. You immediately get all the safe payouts for the remaining days and can no longer pursue the risky project.

Press space bar to continue
